targets.query: SELECT sum("bytes_client"), + sum("bytes_server") FROM "tcp_4_tuple" WHERE ("client_ip" =~ /^$ip$/ OR "server_ip" =~ /^$ip$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($resolution), "server_ip", "client_ip" fill(0)

SELECT sum("bytes_client") + sum("bytes_server")  FROM "tcp_4_tuple" WHERE ("client_ip" =~ /^$ip$/ or "server_ip" =~ /^$ip$/ ) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($resolution), "server_ip", "client_ip" fill(none)

SELECT max("bytes_client_session_max") + max("bytes_server_session_max") FROM "tcp_active_sessions_4_tuple" WHERE ("client_ip" =~ /^$ip$/ or "server_ip" =~ /^$ip$/ )  AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($resolution), "server_ip", "client_ip" fill(none)

SELECT max("bytes_client_session_max") AS "Client Bytes" FROM "tcp_active_sessions_4_tuple" WHERE ("network_monitor_name" =~ /^$network_monitor$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($resolution), "server_ip", "client_ip" fill(0)
